quran[10{c,v,t}:
38,17,( ae paighambar ) yeh jo kuch kehte hain is par sabr karo. aur hamaray bande dawod ko yaad karo jo sahib qowat they ( aur ) be shak woh rujoo karne walay they
38,18,hum ne pahoron ko un ke zair farmaan kardiya tha ke subah vsham un ke sath ( khuday-e ) pak ( ka ) zikar karte they
38,19,aur parindon ko bhi ke jama rehtay they. sab un ke farmanbardar they
38,20,aur hum ne un ki badshahi ko mustahkamkiya aur un ko hikmat ataa ki aur ( khusumat ki ) baat ka faisla ( sikhaya )
38,21,bhala tumahray paas un jhagrnay walon ki bhi khabar aayi hai jab woh deewar phaand kar ibadat khanaay mein daakhil hue
38,22,jis waqt woh dawod ke paas aeye to woh un se ghabra gay unhon ne kaha ke khauf nah kijiye. hum dono ka aik muqadma hai ke hum mein se aik ne dosray par zayad-ti ki hai to aap hum mein insaaf ka faisla kar dijiye aur be insafi nah kijiye ga aur hum ko seedha rasta dikha dijiye
38,23,( kefiyat yeh hai ke ) yeh mera bhai hai is ke ( haan ) ninanway dumbiyan hain aur mere ( paas ) aik dumbi hai. yeh kehta hai ke yeh bhi mere hawalay kardey aur guftagu mein mujh par zabardasti karta hai
38,24,unhon ne kaha ke yeh jo teri dunbi mangta hai ke apni dumbiyon mein milale be shak tujh par zulm karta hai. aur aksar shareek aik dosray par zayad-ti hikiya karte hain. haan jo imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay aur aisay log bohat kam hain. aur dawod ne khayaalkiya ke ( is waqeye se ) hum ne un ko aazmaaya hai to unhon ne apne perwar-digaar se mughfirat mangi aur jhuk kar gur parre aur ( khuda ki taraf ) rujookiya
38,25,to hum ne un ko bakhash diya. aur be shak un ke liye hamaray haan qurb aur umdah maqam hai
38,26,ae dawod hum ne tum ko zameen mein badshah banaya hai to logon mein insaaf ke faislaykiya karo aur khwahish ki pairwi nah karna ke woh tumhe khuda ke raste se bhatka day gi. jo log khuda ke raste se bhataktay hain un ke liye sakht azaab ( tayyar ) hai ke unhon ne hisaab ke din ko bhala diya
